      <abstract>
Records, 1961-1971, of the Office of Student Community Relations of the University of Michigan, organization within the Office of Student Affairs; contain files largely relating to university regulations respecting student use of automobiles and bicycles, student housing, and other student concerns.  Also contains earlier material inherited from other university offices.
</abstract>
